**/node_modules/
staged/
__pycache__/
*.pyc
.DS_Store
*.log
store/
*.db
*.sqlite

# A1 patcher backups
*.bak-*

# _A3_SANITIZE_AND_CLA_V1 -- memory + audit file defence in depth
**/memory/MEMORY.md
**/memory/sessions.md
**/memory/feedback_*.md
**/memory/project_*.md
**/memory/reference_*.md
**/agent_log
**/agent_log.jsonl
**/audit*.log
**/audit-events.jsonl
**/*.token*.json
**/*-cache.json
**/memory.db
**/memory.db-*
**/audit*.db
**/audit*.db-*
**/snapshots/

# _A6_2_LOCAL_ONLY_PATTERNS_V1 -- sanitize patterns/allowlist MUST live only
# at ~/.config/pandoras-box/ (per hooks/pre-push). Belt-and-braces: even if
# someone tries to drop one at the repo root, this gitignore line ensures
# it never gets staged or committed.
.sanitize-patterns
.sanitize-allowlist
.sanitize-patterns.*
.sanitize-allowlist.*
